data.description: Attractive 4.125% assumable~Golf Course beauty! Fresh updates throughout this one-story home in security gated community. Recent updates include fresh interior paint, primary and secondary bathroom with new cabinets, counters, landscaping, new laminate flooring in secondary bedrooms, new roof, new stove and more. Floor plan offers special features including formal extended entry with art niches, Study with French doors, lovely island kitchen w/ open views of golf course and family room. Private master with golf course view. Amazing therapeutic tub benefiting: Relaxes whole body/mind, Relieves pain in sore muscles/joints, Assists detoxification. Many splendid views of golf course!! Backyard patio with pavers and electric shade. If you play golf or not you will love the relaxing views any time of year(very few golf balls). MASTER planned community with this section gated. Amenities included!!Splash pad, swimming pools, parks, lakes, tennis and more. Houston National Golf course!
